OL,3,CRiots 'severely impacted' shopper
OL,4,Cfootfall in early August
OL,6,FRiots across the UK earlier this month
OL,7,F"severely impacted" shopper footfall
OL,8,Fas many consumers stayed away from
OL,9,Fshops and retail parks during the
OL,10,Fviolent unrest, according to a report.
OL,12,FLatest figures from the British Retail
OL,13,FConsortium (BRC)-Sensormatic IQ
OL,14,Frevealed that UK footfall fell 0.4% in
OL,15,FAugust, dropping for the 13th month in
OL,16,Fa row.
