OL,3,CRiots 'severely impacted' shopper
OL,4,Cfootfall in early August
OL,6,FSome cities fared worse than others,
OL,7,Fwith footfall tumbling by 8.1% in
OL,8,FBirmingham while Bristol and Cardiff
OL,9,Fsaw declines of 4.2% and 4.1%
OL,10,Frespectively.
OL,12,FFootfall also fell 3.6% in Nottingham
OL,13,Fand was 1.9% down in Liverpool.
OL,15,FThe summer riots were seen in parts of
OL,16,FBritain earlier this month in the wake
OL,17,Fof the stabbings in Southport.
