OL,3,CRiots 'severely impacted' shopper
OL,4,Cfootfall in early August
OL,6,FThe data showed that footfall bounced
OL,7,Fback in retail parks in the week
OL,8,Ffollowing the riots, helping it rise
OL,9,F2.6% overall throughout August in out-
OL,10,Fof-town destinations as some shoppers
OL,11,Fcontinued to avoid high streets and
OL,12,Fshopping centres.
OL,14,FFootfall then rebounded strongly
OL,15,Facross all shopping destinations at
OL,16,Fthe end of the month, thanks to warmer
OL,17,Fweather and summer discounting,
OL,18,Faccording to the report.
