OL,3,CRiots 'severely impacted' shopper
OL,4,Cfootfall in early August
OL,6,FHelen Dickinson, chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe BRC, said: "As violent disorder
OL,8,Ferupted across the country earlier in
OL,9,Fthe month, footfall was severely
OL,10,Fimpacted as many people stayed away
OL,11,Ffrom shopping destinations."
OL,13,FShe called on the Government to help
OL,14,Fthe retail sector with an overhaul of
OL,15,Fbusiness rates at the upcoming October
OL,16,FBudget.
OL,18,FShe said: "While year-on-year footfall
OL,19,Fchanges improved on July, they remain
OL,20,Fin negative territory.
