OL,6,F"Local communities need Government to
OL,7,Fimplement its high streets plan to
OL,8,Fhelp drive footfall back into growth.
OL,10,F"The upcoming budget is an opportunity
OL,11,Fto move forward with the plan to fix
OL,12,Fthe broken business rates system which
OL,13,Facts as a brake on retail investment,
OL,14,Fand contributes to our declining high
OL,15,Fstreets as it leads to so many store
OL,16,Fclosures up and down the country."
